name: October 9, 2011
description: Original painting by Laura Guese. Gouache and soft pastel on watercolor paper, measuring 8 x 8 inches. Painting is matted in an archival white mat, outer dimensions measuring 12 x 12. Packaged in a protective plastic sleeve. Fits nicely into a 12 x 12 frame. Signed and dated on the front and back. This painting is part of my One Sky One Year project where I am painting the sky everyday for 365 days. This painting reflects fleeting atmospheric conditions, and the emotions evoked by the sky.
